00:32:29.699 --> 00:32:30.700
Ouah !

424
00:32:59.896 --> 00:33:01.481
Merci, vieux !

425
00:33:02.982 --> 00:33:04.067
De rien !

426
00:33:08.196 --> 00:33:09.322
Oui, Pete.

427
00:33:09.405 --> 00:33:12.408
PONT
À 1 KM

428
00:33:26.506 --> 00:33:27.507
Allez !

429
00:33:29.133 --> 00:33:31.010
On l'a, Pete.

